 'Quiet Moon':{glyph:'☾',tones:['Low-gravity hush','Crater glow','Unfinished orbit'],texts:['Silence has a clean horizon today. Empty slots are holding their shape without apology.','The moon is bright with things not said yet; drafts may float before they decide to land.','Low gravity favors incomplete thoughts. Let one pause remain permanent enough to guide someone.']}
